Chile Home-Building Permits Increased in August

-- B y   D o m i n i c   C a r e y
-- 
2011-09-29T12:07:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/chile-home-building-permits-increased-in-august-table-.html
Chilean building permits for new 
 home construction  increased in Aug. according to the National
Statistics Institute in Santiago.  The number of homes approved for construction rose 37.1
percent in Aug. to 9,955, compared to 7,259 a year earlier. 
